---
description: Draft three complete implementation plans, score them, pick the best, then code.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Before coding, create **three end‑to‑end plans** covering:
  - architecture & libraries
  - complexity, maintainability, performance, security
- Score each plan 1‑5 in those four areas.
- Pick the highest total score and justify the choice in ≤ 150 words.
- Only then may implementation begin.
